data.description: Looking for one level living w/ a bonus loft? You found it ~ 3 BR's and 2 BA's on the entry level w/ another 1/2 BA in the bonus loft. Move in ready with fresh paint throughout and newly refinished hardwood floors. Next you'll find a spacious open kitchen appointed with matching stainless steel appliances and other beautiful touches. The great room with lofted ceiling is sure to please along with the stone facia fireplace. The primary BR suite w/ BA is located on one side, and the two other spacious BR's w/ BA are located on the other side of the home. We can't forget about that spiral staircase that will take you to a BONUS loft that is sure to offer the creative with endless possibilities...BR, office, or study. New full HVAC system replaced just 2 years ago to keep you freshly heated or cooled. Outside provides a front porch, rear deck, rolling yet mostly level fenced in rear yard, and utility shed. Welcome to 3577 Overbrook DR and Welcome Home!
